#: ../../source/methods/adaptation.rst:1
msgid "Adaptation"
msgstr "适应"

#: ../../source/methods/adaptation.rst:3
msgid ""
"Transfer calibration models between instruments or correct for "
"differences in spectral axes. Adaptation methods ensure that models "
"trained on one instrument remain valid when applied to another, reducing "
"the need for expensive recalibration campaigns."
msgstr ""
"在仪器之间传递校准模型，或纠正光谱轴的差异。适应方法确保在一台仪器上训练的模型在"
"应用于另一台仪器时仍然有效，从而减少昂贵的重新校准工作的需求。"
